text: Nestled on a quiet cul de sac on a heavily treed lot, this stunning family home is sure to impress! Upon entering you are greeted by an impressive sweeping staircase and large picture windows that draw the eye to the enchanting, park-like setting. With easy access to Hwy 121, minutes to Parr Park, DFW Airport and schools, the location cannot be beat; this family residence is a true gem!

text: Come see this spacious, updated and completely move in ready home with a fabulous floorplan. Home has new flooring, granite counter tops, new modern light fixtures, fresh paint, blinds, etc. Main living areas are downstairs with living room, dining room, kitchen, half bath, laundry and a multipurpose room currently used as a mud room and office space. The backyard has a nice deck for entertainment and a small yard space for a pet. This home is in a wonderful location close to downtown Grapevine, shopping, entertainment and a quick trip to DFW airport or enjoy an evening walk to Dove Park. Don't wait! This home won't last long!

Fantastic, single story home located in the highly sought after Grapevine-Colleyville ISD. This adorable home is nestled in a quiet cul de sac and features an open floor plan with gorgeous vinyl flooring throughout the home installed in the spring of 2024. Tax records show this as a 3 bedroom home. Office does not have a closet so this would be a true 2 bedroom with an office. Updated kitchen offers granite countertops, subway tile backsplash, farmhouse sink, whirlpool gas range(installed fall of 2021), whirlpool dishwasher(winter of 2022) and new whirlpool microwave the end of 2024. Large primary bedroom with ensuite bath has been completely remodeled with modern updates to include a frameless walk in tiled shower with bench seating, dual sink vanity, updated light fixtures, and amazing tile flooring completed in the fall of 2021. Secondary full bath was also completely remodeled in 2021. Trane HVAC system was installed in the fall of 2023. Don't miss the large Backyard oasis with hottub! Relax under the awning with turf grass or on the spacious deck perfect for entertaining. Enjoy quiet evenings sitting by the firepit. Conveniently located close to Dove elemtary school, parks, dining, shopping, highways, downtown Grapevine and Grapevine Lake!! Don't miss your chance to call this one home!!

text: Nestled in the heart of the vibrant city of Grapevine, this exceptional lot offers the perfect blend of location and convenience. Located downtown, one block from charming Historic Main Street, you'll have easy access to Grapevine's renowned shopping, dining, local wineries and entertainment options, as well as top-rated schools, parks and Grapevine Lake. Grapevine is a commuter's paradise, strategically located in the center of the Dallas-Fort Worth metroplex. With major highway access and home to DFW International Airport, this location offers unparalleled convenience. Additionally, Downtown Grapevine is a hub for the TexRail commuter train, connecting directly to DFW Airport in seven minutes, and providing commuters easy access from Fort Worth and cities in between. This accessibility makes it ideal for both business and residential development, offering immense potential for future growth. This 14, 923 sq. ft. lot is currently zoned Commercial, with potential for residential development after approval from Grapevine's Planning and Zoning. There is the possibility to subdivide the lot into two residential parcels, offering a rare opportunity to build one's dream home. Take advantage of the local wineries, scenic lake, and rich history that make Grapevine a unique and desirable destination. Don't let this rare opportunity pass you by-this property is waiting for you to make it your own! Buyer and Buyer Agent to verify all information required for development with the City of Grapevine.

text: Welcome to the Millican House, a one-of-a-kind luxury home in the Historic District, walking distance from Main Street. Originally built in 1935 as a Sears kit house, this property has been carefully preserved and rebuilt into an approximately 3, 935 square foot masterpiece. The current homeowners have thoughtfully preserved portions of the original house, adding to the charm and character of this stunning home. This property boasts four bedrooms and four bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. The primary bedroom, study and an open floor plan built for entertaining are all conveniently located on the first floor. The guest house features a living area, bathroom and bedroom, perfect for hosting guests or as a private retreat. Venture outside and enjoy the refreshing cocktail pool, outdoor kitchen and living center, surrounded by plenty of lawn space for play. With its prime location in the Historic District, this property offers a unique opportunity to own a piece of history while enjoying modern amenities and comforts. We invite you to come and see this stunning property for yourself. Welcome home!

text: Foundation work to be completed with a lifetime warranty Discover the epitome of comfort & elegance in this stunning townhome nestled in Grapevine, TX. As you step inside, you'll immediately feel the warmth & charm that makes this home a true haven. Boasting thoughtful upgrades such as a brand-new range, dishwasher, & microwave. The layout is perfectly designed for both privacy & socializing. It features 2 bedrooms, thoughtfully split to ensure personal space. The open dining and living area, complete with a cozy wood-burning fireplace & an inviting wet bar, creates an ideal environment for entertaining guests or a quiet evening at home. On the 2 floor find yourself in a private sanctuary that is the primary bedroom. This spacious retreat includes 2 walk-in closets & ensuite bathroom! Situated in an enviable location, this home is just moments away from the serene Grapevine Lake & a few blocks from the vibrant historic downtown Main Street.

Beautiful large David Weekley home in desirable Silver Lakes Estates. This home is the model plan & has every sf option that could be added including, bonus room over garage, super utility, media room & 5th bedroom. Upgraded curb appeal plus thoughtful design throughout make this a perfect home. The large bright living room features a fireplace with custom wood mantle to the second floor. The living area flows to the kitchen featuring granite, SS appliances including a warming drawer. The dedicated private office features French doors with a transom, floor to ceiling custom bookshelves & woodwork. Upstairs has many options with 3 bedrooms, a media room and a oversized bonus room with built in seating and storage. Exemplary Grapevine Colleyville ISD schools. Fantastic location located within walking distance to historic downtown and lake Grapevine. Ease of access to shopping, dining, DFW airport.

text: This one-of-a-kind, needle-in-a-haystack wooded lot is located on a hill in the charming town of Grapevine, Texas. Nestled among towering trees, this lot offers unparalleled privacy and tranquility. Located seconds from the best park in Grapevine, Parr Park, this lot is a nature lover's dream come true. The park boasts miles of hiking trails, sports fields, and a stunning nature preserve, sport courts, splash pad, and playground equipment. This lot offers the perfect combination of privacy and convenience. It's situated in a quiet, secluded area, yet it's just minutes from all the amenities and attractions that Grapevine has to offer. With easy access to major highways, this lot is ideal for anyone looking for a peaceful retreat that's still within easy reach of the city. This 1-acre wooded lot is a true gem that's sure to appeal to anyone looking for a one-of-a-kind property in the heart of Grapevine. This lot is the perfect place to build your dream home and create a lifetime of memories.
